careMain.Rd

Medicare Endpoint

Medicare Endpoint 2

Usage

careMain(alias)

careMain2(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <careMain> object.

An S7 <careMain> object.

Examples

if (FALSE) { # interactive()
careMain("contact")
careMain("crosswalk")
careMain("dialysis")
careMain("enrollees")
careMain("facilities")
careMain("hospice_acute")
careMain("IQIES")
careMain("laboratories")
careMain("long_term")
careMain("opt_out")
careMain("order_refer")
careMain("rbcs")
careMain("transparency")
}
